source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05401_000010_GAIA<tab>I'm drawing out the Darkness. Get ready!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05401_000010_GAIA<tab>I'm drawing out the Darkness. Get ready!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05401_000020_RYNE<tab>It worked, Gaia! We've done it!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05401_000020_RYNE<tab>It worked, Gaia! We've done it!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05401_000030_RYNE<tab>So this all took place a hundred years ago...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05401_000030_RYNE<tab>So this all took place a hundred years ago...

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05401_000040_RYNE<tab>But what does it have to do with Gaia?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05401_000040_RYNE<tab>But what does it have to do with Gaia?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05401_000050_RYNE<tab>I know this place...! It's the gaol in Eulmore!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05401_000050_RYNE<tab>I know this place...! It's the gaol in Eulmore!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05401_000070_RYNE<tab>...we will never give up hope!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05401_000070_RYNE<tab>...we will never give up hope!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05401_000100_EDEN3BOSS4<tab>One that we may share for all eternity.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05401_000100_EDEN3BOSS4<tab>One that we may share for all eternity.

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05401_000120_RYNE<tab>I won't give up on our future, Gaia! No matter what!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_05401_000120_RYNE<tab>I won't give up on our future, Gaia! No matter what!
